 A few centuries after that, star-star rapid travel on interstellar magnetic accelerated ships (rings of accelerator coils, powered by a K-2 civilization's solar collectors. Toss ships up to .95C, to be decelerated at the destination star.) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=513.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=513.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=513.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=513.topic&start=81&stop=95>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=513.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=513.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=513.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.nuclearspace.com/ezboard/images/addreply3.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=513.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.threadControl?topicID=513.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=513.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.